results.name: Decimal expansion of (2+sqrt(5))/2.
comment: Continued fraction expansion of (2+sqrt(5))/2 is A010698.
formula: equals (2 + sqrt(5))/2 = 1/2 + phi, with phi = A001622.
xref: Cf. A002163 (decimal expansion of sqrt(5)), A020837 (decimal expansion of 1/sqrt(80)), A010698 (repeat 2, 8).
